<item>
            <title>[SUREFIRE-501] -Xmx JVM option is not used by the surefire process</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SUREFIRE-501</link>
                <project id="12317927" key="SUREFIRE">Maven Surefire (Moved to GitHub Issues)</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;I use the jvm option &lt;b&gt;&quot;-Xmx1024m&quot;&lt;/b&gt; to execute maven 2.0.9. I&apos;ve got heavy integration tests.&lt;br/&gt;
When the process surefire forks, it does not use this option. His maximum heap size is only 65 MB.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment>Windows XP SP2, JDK 1.6, Maven 2.0.9, surefire 2.4.2</environment>
        <key id="12810160">SUREFIRE-501</key>
            <summary>-Xmx JVM option is not used by the surefire process</summary>
